  "analyst_note": "CVE-2003-0694: Remote root buffer overflow in Sendmail 8.12.9 and earlier via the prescan() function processing SMTP envelope addresses. Nmap -sV reliably extracts the Sendmail version from the SMTP ESMTP banner (220 hostname ESMTP Sendmail X.Y.Z). If a non-Sendmail MTA is detected (Postfix, Exim, qmail, Exchange), mark as not validated. If Sendmail is confirmed at a vulnerable version, this is a critical finding though historical.",
